{"id": 2016, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些游乐园体验会让你觉得“天啊我为什么会来这儿”！", "description": "你有哪些难忘的“游乐场玩我”时刻？", "record_count": 2308, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201711161036522Z0LSn7IDXwad4Fj.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-27T03:00:54Z", "options": [{"id": 251136, "content": "里面的东西太贵比外面贵一半，而且游乐设施还不好玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194840}, {"id": 251137, "content": "各种动画、超级英雄主题的项目进去发现全是过山车！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144138}, {"id": 251138, "content": "只有我一个人觉得迪士尼乐园非常无聊且幼稚吗…16岁去的洛杉矶迪士尼乐园  进去了除了拍照就是看自家国人人挤人  好不容易排上了  但你确定这种规模的游乐设施真的不是给小学生玩的吗?", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887423}, {"id": 251394, "content": "“游乐园”这三个字本身就已经是我的雷区了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064223}, {"id": 251139, "content": "“激流勇进”排队三小时，防水衣没穿好，裤子湿透。正巧生理期……", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957352}, {"id": 251140, "content": "排队排到怀疑人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125750}, {"id": 251141, "content": "刺激到变成一次性买卖?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831486}, {"id": 251142, "content": "这种活动太复古了 完全么兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786689}, {"id": 251143, "content": "队友不跟我去玩刺激的", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195746}, {"id": 254727, "content": "人海", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086674}, {"id": 251144, "content": "很多很多熊猫抱着竹子的垃圾桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877992}, {"id": 251145, "content": "过山车上到最高处的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195766}, {"id": 251146, "content": "满目皆是气球射击，套圈圈赢奖品等低幼复古项目。且奖品都是样式变异，千奇百怪版本的五六十年代玩具。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867244}, {"id": 251147, "content": "当我身处一堆小孩中时，我不禁在旋转木马上陷入沉思", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155587}, {"id": 251404, "content": "坐个一分多钟的过山车，排队俩小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156449}, {"id": 251149, "content": "在鸣沙山月牙泉体验一次爬沙漠", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115890}, {"id": 251150, "content": "排不到头的队伍，难吃的食物以及数不清的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195776}, {"id": 251151, "content": "晕车的我第二个项目坐了过山车\n然后一个下午就这么报废了\n什么都没得玩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192182}, {"id": 252943, "content": "卡卡龙哦哦哦我我想问一下", "image": "img/option/option/20171206224418bNCGnUlRsctBxid1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182699}, {"id": 251152, "content": "排队的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 251153, "content": "下雨了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156386}, {"id": 251154, "content": "毫无意义的人工虚构商业模式景点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 251155, "content": "游乐园。。项目时间剧短。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 251156, "content": "排队五小时，使用两分钟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 251157, "content": "都是人还小孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319841}, {"id": 251413, "content": "一群糟心的小屁孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197253}, {"id": 251158, "content": "除了过山车还是过山车，幼稚！", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636498}, {"id": 251670, "content": "太多人人人人人人人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094341}, {"id": 251159, "content": "单看游乐园这三个字就不想去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467780}, {"id": 251160, "content": "游乐园变成旅游景点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979933}, {"id": 251161, "content": "好不容易排到之后。。。啊啊啊啊啊啊我死也不想再玩这个了!!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194754}, {"id": 252441, "content": "情侣…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202749}, {"id": 251163, "content": "从刺激，变成，一次，性买卖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689835}, {"id": 251168, "content": "去哪个项目都能碰到腻腻歪歪的情侣  还穿着校服 哼", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066613}, {"id": 251169, "content": "人…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915230}, {"id": 257825, "content": "连续被同一个角色两次索吻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228841}, {"id": 251170, "content": "应该是独游吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050030}, {"id": 251171, "content": "我去过一次燕山公园，里面的滑梯、丛林鼠、空中脚踏车仿佛回到了80年代。除了一开始的怀旧然后满是尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 254755, "content": "动物园，坚决不去第二次", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992026}, {"id": 251172, "content": "排队！人多！小孩多！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191545}, {"id": 251173, "content": "没有女朋友 自己一个人排长长的队", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195889}, {"id": 251174, "content": "这个坏了那个关了剩下好多人的.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115056}, {"id": 249130, "content": "项目不是刺激度太高就是太低幼，没有可以玩的适中设备", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 251178, "content": "买了游园车票，结果发现走下来顶多半个小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 249131, "content": "不是花车游行就是打枪抓娃娃，仿佛仍走在上个世纪的游乐场", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 251179, "content": "别人都有对像……而我领着弟弟来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188499}, {"id": 249132, "content": "说是主题公园，但只有满大街的套头娃娃跟主题有关", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 251180, "content": "排队的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194794}, {"id": 249134, "content": "游客占位拍照，拍打扮演人偶的工作人员", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 251182, "content": "能解决j", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188810}]}